        <li>Discuss time management strategies, setting priorities and overcoming obstacles.</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Time Management Strategies</h4>
      <ol>
        <li>Maintain a calendar.</li>
        <li>Make a daily to-do list.</li>
        <li>Stay organized.</li>
        <li>Set a timer.</li>
        <li>Divide larger projects into smaller assignments.</li>
        <li>Knock out the hard tasks first. </li>
        <li>Combine similar tasks.</li>
        <li>Study when you have the most amount of energy.</li>
        <li>Study in short blocks of time throughout the day.</li>
        <li>Be flexible, determined and patient.</li>
      </ol>   
